57:13.388 --> 57:15.557
♪ In a one-horse-open sleigh ♪

57:15.640 --> 57:18.143
♪ O'er the fields we go ♪

57:18.226 --> 57:20.478
♪ Laughing all the way ♪

57:20.562 --> 57:22.814
♪ Bells on bobtails ring ♪

57:22.897 --> 57:24.816
♪ Making spirits bright ♪

57:24.899 --> 57:27.235
♪ What fun it is to ride and sing ♪

57:27.318 --> 57:29.612
♪ A sleighing song tonight ♪

57:29.696 --> 57:32.157
